Full screen mode makes it simple for you to use <%= pne %> without
any distractions. Follow these steps to enable full screen mode.

1. Select **Enter Full Screen** from the **View** menu.
   ![view menu](all-menu-view){: .menu_dropshadow}

2. Alternatively you can use the shortcut key as shown in the **View** menu.

3. You can also use the standard <%= mac_os %> document window title bar
   control to start full screen.
   ![fullscreen](all-docpart-windowcontrols)
